Install Flask and BeaitufulSoul
pip install flask
pip install beautifulsoup4
pip install requests

Create the Flask app: app.py (code from set)

Run python app.py

Access the Website with fun facts: Open your web browser and go to http://127.0.0.1:5000/

Flask: This is a lightweight WSGI web application framework in Python.
BeautifulSoup and Requests: These libraries are used to scrape online content.
local_facts: A list of local fun facts.
get_online_fun_fact(): This function scrapes fun facts from an online source.
home(): This is the route for the home page. It randomly selects whether to show a local or an online fun fact.
